snippet: Eight people face federal charges of illegally trafficking paddlefish caviar from a prime paddlefish location in western Missouri after an investigation that spanned nine states and several years.
lead_paragraph: Eight people face federal charges of illegally trafficking paddlefish caviar from a prime paddlefish location in western Missouri after an investigation that spanned nine states and several years.

headline.main: Missouri: 8 Face Charges in Illegal Trafficking of Paddlefish Caviar
